titles.title: A bill to designate the Department of Veterans Affairs outpatient clinic in Wenatchee, Washington, as the Elwood "Bud" Link Department of Veterans Affairs Outpatient Clinic.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S5872)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Veterans' Affairs.

bill.summary:
5/9/2007--Introduced.
Designates the Department of Veterans Affairs outpatient clinic in Wenatchee, Washington, as the "Elwood 'Bud' Link Department of Veterans Affairs Outpatient Clinic."
